cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.NE 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language processing and word sense disambiguation. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper discusses the use of supervised learning algorithms and the impact of different types of features on machine learning methods. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is another possible category as the paper deals with identifying the proper sense of ambiguous words in text. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper discusses the use of machine learning methods for natural language processing tasks. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is also a possible category as the paper discusses the use of recurrent neural networks based on Long-Short Term Memory nodes.
